        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\nactor Patient\nparticipant \&quot;Hospital System\&quot; as System\ndatabase \&quot;Database\&quot; as DB\nentity \&quot;Appointment\&quot; as Appointment\n\n== Login Flow ==\nPatient -&gt; System: log into system\nactivate System\nSystem -&gt; DB: validate credentials\nactivate DB\nDB --&gt; System: valid/invalid\ndeactivate DB\nalt not valid\n  System --&gt; Patient: enter valid info\nelse valid\n  System --&gt; Patient: validated\nend\ndeactivate System\n\n== Appointment Booking ==\nPatient -&gt; System: search doctor by specialty\nactivate System\nSystem -&gt; DB: fetch doctor list\nactivate DB\nDB --&gt; System: doctor list\ndeactivate DB\nSystem --&gt; Patient: display doctors\ndeactivate System\n\nPatient -&gt; System: select time slot\nactivate System\nPatient -&gt; System: submit appointment request\nSystem -&gt; DB: check availability\nactivate DB\nalt not available\n  DB --&gt; System: slot unavailable\n  System --&gt; Patient: choose another slot\nelse available\n  DB --&gt; System: slot confirmed\n  System -&gt; Appointment: create appointment\n  activate Appointment\n  Appointment --&gt; System: appointment object\n  deactivate Appointment\n  System --&gt; Patient: appointment confirmation\nend\ndeactivate DB\ndeactivate System\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="S88kijV71PueXaDN08IK-1">
